restaurant.description: A pinch of Italy, a dash of France and a dose of New York City and you have our cozy & warm style Fiat Cafe! We only use organic eggs and all-natural chicken.

top_review.review_text: I have never been disappointed in any meal I have ordered here. The food is absolutely amazing.
